└── modern-card (overflow: visible) ← 允许滚动条显示
    └── list_texts (overflow: visible) ← 允许滚动条显示
        └── scrollable-list (overflow-y: auto) ← 实际滚动容器
            └── modern-list (无overflow设置) ← 内容容器
```

